{"tid":257922,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"信和玩具店涉搞「一番賞」    警拉男店主","createTime":"2017-05-25T15:36:28.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-27T08:27:40.000Z","uid":48093,"like":4,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"05c9019e0814d1b7f0281e59324dd2556e12550a","tid":257922,"uid":48093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T15:36:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170525/large/1495724389_fef3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170525%2Flarge%2F1495724389_fef3.jpg&h=595e55b7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n旺角警區雜項調查隊人員根據線報，今日下午3時30分採取行動，派員喬裝顧客，在旺角彌敦道信和中心一店鋪拘捕一名34歲姓莊男店鋪負責人，涉嫌「經營非法獎券活動」。行動中，警員撿獲一批證物，包括抽獎券、抽獎箱、海報及相關獎品等。據悉，涉事的玩具店涉嫌舉辦日本流行的「一番賞」抽獎活動。<br />\n<br />\n警方經初步調查，相信該店鋪未有申領相關牌照，舉行抽獎活動。如顧客想獲得指定獎品，需要先購買指定貨品，才可獲得一次抽取該獎品的機會。"},{"pid":"68265d0bb5dd5246c76075c0a2fdd5cdbe55bf38","tid":257922,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T15:37:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e54a4d029b085f787bd5b813ccd7187829fbf8c","tid":257922,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T15:38:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56f7747bfef66c27a5985eb0caf1bef2ae6b4bbe","tid":257922,"uid":51200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T15:39:08.000Z","msg":"聽frd講間野個中奬率奇低<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n懷疑俾客報寸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e98f1bda7e3fa13d66cca33b8b1f787cee1dd71c","tid":257922,"uid":22700,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T